    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "React is not the good tool if we are to just manipulate an input. jQuery or VanillaJS? \n\nTruth is, do we even need rendering for a search input? Is the search box a widget, or an enhanced dom element? Do we want enhanced elements, wouldn't it create inconsistencies between the search box and the rest?\n\nImho, that's a very edge case and should be low priority.\n",
