    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I am against having a distinction on hosting our widgets in the .widgets namespace or in the instantsearch configuration based on wheter or not it's an empty element. Or an element we reuse.\n\nI feel we are moving it in the instantsearch constructor because on the implementation side, it seems more obvious.\n\nBut on a usage side, I will look for the searchBox widget in .widgets, not in the instantSearch configuration.\n\nWhat do you think?\n",
