    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I would keep the searchBox in the .widget namespace.\n\nRegarding the wrapping div/input discussion, what I would do is add a new input if the dom element given is not already an input, and directly enhance it with our listening events if it is. For this widget the only markup we need (an `input`) is one that is likely already in the page, let's use it.\n",
